    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a high heat</p><p>Trim, then chop your <strong>spring onion[s]</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
