          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the meat-free mince is cooking, cut your <strong>lime[s]</strong> in half</p><p>Roughly chop your <strong>coriander</strong>, including the stalks</p><p>Strip your <strong>mint leaves</strong> from their stems and chop them roughly, discard the stems</p><p>Cut your <strong>red chilli[es]</strong> in half lengthways, deseed (scrape the seeds out with a teaspoon) and slice roughly</p>",
