      "instruction": "<p>Squeeze the pouch[es] of <strong>cooked white long grain rice</strong> to separate the grains</p><p>Add your<strong> cooked white long grain rice</strong> and<strong> ginger & garlic paste</strong> to the<strong> </strong>browned meat-free mince and cook for 2-3 min, breaking the rice up with a wooden spoon as you go</p>",
