    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>soy sauce</strong>,<strong> </strong>the juice of<strong> half</strong> your<strong> lime[s]</strong>, <strong>sesame oil</strong>, <strong>shredded lettuce</strong>, <strong>sliced chilli </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!), <strong>mint</strong> and <strong>coriander</strong> to the pan and give it a good mix up – this is your<strong> larb filling</strong></p><p>Cut the<strong> remaining lime</strong> into 1 wedge per person</p>",
